{
  "text": "The nodal comparisons are totally in harmony with the above discussions of Figures 9 and 10 . Especially the viscosity (m) values, at the mid-location (x ¼ 2.5 cm) of the bearing, put forward the notable role of temperature on lubricant viscosity with a decay rate of 29.2% (1.484806À1.051918 Pas), which show parallelism with the records of Fang et al. [CITATION_1] .",
